# Raw photo dumps (uncurated, full-resolution camera originals): never commit
# these. Curate + compress into src/assets/<pasta>/ under a proper filename
# instead. As of 2026-07-16 the raw Diálogos folders live one level above the
# repo, in ../dialogos-fotos-originais-nao-usadas/ — this rule is a backstop
# in case a similar raw dump ever lands inside src/assets/ again.
src/assets/**/FOTOS*/
src/assets/**/Fotos*/
